&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ogsc=&quot;black&quot;&gt;For overall team productivity, we optimize meeting hours in the pacific time zone. We avoid scheduling recurring meetings that start after 3pm PT, however, ad hoc meetings occur between 8am-6pm Pacific time. &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;#LI-remote&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
