&lt;p&gt;Truveta is the world’s first health provider led data platform with a vision of Saving Lives with Data. Our mission is to enable researchers to find cures faster, empower every clinician to be an expert, and help families make the most informed decisions about their care. Achieving Truveta’ s ambitious vision requires an incredible team of talented and inspired people with a special combination of health, software and big data experience who share our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.truveta.com/careers/&quot;&gt;company values&lt;/a&gt;. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
